#: commands.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Menu"
msgstr "Меню «Зміни»"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&symboleditor; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu items, for "
"more information read the sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"menus.html#menus-edit\">Edit Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
